messages.content:
Namaste, Divya. Aapka prashna sun kar achha laga. Shaddi ka vichar mann mein aana, ek natural baat hai. "Iss saal ho jayegi meri shaddi?" – This is a very important question for you, I understand.

Dekho, Divya, abhi aapki Venus dasha chal rahi hai. Venus, prem aur vivah ka grah hai, toh yeh dasha shaddi ke liye bahut important hoti hai. And Venus is in the 7th house, that's excellent! The 7th house is all about partnership and marriage.

Lekin, Divya, exactly kab hogi, yeh batane ke liye mujhe aapki kundali ke aur details chahiye honge – especially your ascendant, ki aapka lagn kya hai? Aur Jupiter aur Saturn ki current position bhi dekhni hogi.

Ultimately, I need the full chart details to give you a more accurate prediction. Chinta mat karo. We will try to understand your chart in more detail. Is there any specific date or time of birth you can share so I can help you better?
